{"tid":1583890,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"唱歌就好似玩狩獵笛 唔係冇用 係齋喺後面吹冇乜大用 一路吹一路打先有用","createTime":"2019-09-21T00:34:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T05:48:59.000Z","uid":24814,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3e2ff483dbc8ffa10e72d4798d8b2f190c0ada5d","tid":1583890,"uid":24814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T00:34:34.000Z","msg":"本來個post話「願榮光歸香港」就係一首軍歌<br />\n軍歌就係畀你一路打一路唱增加士氣<br />\n喺後面齋吹狩獵笛冇用 你唔走去扑怪 你就係一個玩得好失敗嘅狩獵笛"},{"pid":"10818b5fafe2bc20aa4d8d0e3f3df7ec11cd5ef4","tid":1583890,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T00:34:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">由於都係有好多人唔明行動有咩意義同目標 於是係正式攻略之前出個簡化版</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【行動】【主線】 【922】【SUCK4.0】 【多圖】 【簡易式攻略目標 】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1583476\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1583476</a>"},{"pid":"4a9bf397705c26871710135f01e772ad5b262309","tid":1583890,"uid":152594,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T00:37:19.000Z","msg":"大大力扑落個頭到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70e88ca4d9f21d833756974e98eae048c5a1a835","tid":1583890,"uid":62837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T00:48:19.000Z","msg":"狩笛要記譜 打頭 兩樣都好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9d8940b45f647d451f9e9670d7ecc1b58e3a242","tid":1583890,"uid":284932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T01:15:39.000Z","msg":"小弟琴晚用 keyboard 練咗國歌喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小弟認為國歌在戶外要有更好效果, 就要好似儀仗隊咁樣<br />\n想簡單啲就, 一群巴絲組織小號樂團奏國歌既 melody, 小號 Trumpet 又俗稱喇(口八)<br />\n前排要有軍鼓樂團, 打一個 bar 既 snare drum solo intro, 之後就喇(口八)在第2個 bar 入<br />\n其他唔識玩樂器既隊友就一齊大合唱<br />\n不過小弟唔識做 band leader 又唔識做 conductor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nany opinion and suggestion?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddc06bd4ee86482c8a403d0ad88a39faa839a2d6","tid":1583890,"uid":24814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70e88ca4d9f21d833756974e98eae048c5a1a835","tid":1583890,"uid":62837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T00:48:19.000Z","msg":"狩笛要記譜 打頭 兩樣都好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T05:48:59.000Z","msg":"記好首歌 兜頭扑落去 就係咁簡單"}]}